{
  "stem": "4272.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Death, immediately.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] You were caught on the train or anywhere else-- anywhere else outside the ghetto, you were killed.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Was everyone given some sort of work to do?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, forced work, sure.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were catching people on-- from their-- from their homes, from the streets.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I would say mostly men.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember them taking any girls that way to work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were-- they really didn't have much work for them, but they beat them up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When they came at the end of the day from work, the family couldn't recognize them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that-- that was going on constantly, every single day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 141,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Were you taken for work at this time?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was not taken for work to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 143,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What about the young children?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 143,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Did they have schooling?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 144,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, with the young children started when they made [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 144,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Plozk, ?] what they said Judenrein.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 144,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In other words, no Jews remained.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 144,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were some people that came out with children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 144,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some came out with infants that they-- they put something around their neck in [INAUDIBLE] to hold up the child in it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 144,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The German would pull it off their neck and throw the child against a tree, against anything that was there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 144,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was right away in '41.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 144,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So no children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 144,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the younger children, when they put us on-- on open trucks, the little children couldn't-- we were pushed so tightly that the little children could not catch their breath, and they arrived at the destination death.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 145,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Did this happen while you were in the ghetto, or when you left the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was after-- after they sent us out from Plozk.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took us there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Was the entire--",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
